</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Secondly, increased claims can result from increased numbers of lawsuits (frivolous or not, that judgment is subjective) and/or an increase in the amount of award per lawsuit. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
