<br />

<br />
This is a statistic I have seen may times; that very few doctors make up the majority of med-mal claims. I am in complete agreement with you when wondering why something more isn't being done about it.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">I wouldn’t argue for any cap that isn’t indexed to inflation. Don’t assign that argument to be by default. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
