				<td valign="middle" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="profile.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=26271&amp;sid=3937a42551fdeda95901cb3c4f05667b"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_profile.gif" alt="View users profile" title="View users profile" border="0" /></a> <a href="privmsg.php?mode=post&amp;u=26271&amp;sid=3937a42551fdeda95901cb3c4f05667b"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_pm.gif" alt="Send private message" title="Send private message" border="0" /></a>     <script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript"><!--

